      • setEmailAlreadyTracked

        public void setEmailAlreadyTracked​(boolean emailAlreadyTracked)
        Sets a boolean indicating if an email address has already be inserted into the email_addresses table in MYSQL for this client when downloading one of the .nii files. This minimizes unnecessary database access since email addresses are unique in the database.
        Parameters:
        emailAlreadyTracked - - boolean
